headline: Governor and Pam Dive More Into State of State Speech
sentences: Dewine joined Canton’s Morning News to break down his main talking points and the progress of the state as a whole.
Stay Tuned daily with Canton’s Morning News for more guests informing you on the state of Ohio and Stark County.
For the first time in two years Governor Mike Dewine delivered Ohio’s State of the State speech.
Pam also had the opportunity to talk about more about Ohio’s pressing issues including Mapping.
